      *======================================
      * TKT1  = BOX QTY
      * 0.7   = BOX U/W                 (KG)
      * TAREW = TOTAL BOX WGT           (KG)
      * PPLT  = PALLET QTY
      * 6.5   = PALLET U/W              (KG)
      * TARE  = TOTAL (BOX + PALLET) WGT(KG)
      * TNET  = TOTAL NET WGT           (KG)
      * TGRS  = TOTAL GROSS WGT         (KG)
      * PNET  = TOTAL NET WGT           (LB)
      * TAREG = TOTAL (BOX + PALLET) WGT(LB)
      * PGRS  = TOTAL GROSS WGT         (LB)
      *=========================================
